Package: tragbR
Title: Max house price calculator
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Christoph", "Zust", , "christoph_zust@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This repository contains a formal model and an implementation for calculating the maximum affordable purchase price of a property based on assets and income. Further parameters required are: Equity requirements, maintenance costs, interest payments, and amortization over a defined period.
